{"tid":1073420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一約連登友出嚟經歷","createTime":"2019-03-22T16:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T17:31:40.000Z","uid":235620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ecdd0732fb79a5bb82910f8117695195494805ac","tid":1073420,"uid":235620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cf270daa911edf478db4e9d60f6058ec6935f9","tid":1073420,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"出到黎成班mk 畀佢地恰"},{"pid":"60d46d479d166c2033404530bcaa4486a88b0c95","tid":1073420,"uid":235620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92cf270daa911edf478db4e9d60f6058ec6935f9","tid":1073420,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"出到黎成班mk 畀佢地恰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"金鐘麥記？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f20bef9827bcc6c4f8a3a55d4372011b71d8e03","tid":1073420,"uid":229519,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"連登友係我女朋友得唔得<br />\nps:女朋友我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6edbfcc74c3d1e08e77c78c57bd87b1e61831fe","tid":1073420,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92cf270daa911edf478db4e9d60f6058ec6935f9","tid":1073420,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"出到黎成班mk 畀佢地恰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"會唔會係咁呀😑"},{"pid":"b4f352a81c3a8210cc3892575de54c130ca378c6","tid":1073420,"uid":204024,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"傾左兩年先約出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢有想約過我 不過我拒絕左 因為我想搵個陌生人9up下咋<br />\n咁佢都冇迫我 大家都好安於純傾計嘅狀況 慢慢咁我好依賴佢 有咩都同佢講 咁佢都會成日同我傾到夜一夜 唔知點解就係有傾唔完嘅野<br />\n到有日唔知傾到啲乜 佢話不如真係約出嚟囉<br />\n可能傾得耐左我都慢慢信任佢 覺得係時候啦 我個下就好衝動咁應承左 <br />\n見到面個下覺得佢比我想像中靚仔 <br />\n個陣心諗 又一個偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲記得個日有啲凍 佢攬住左我 我冇縮開 因為老實講都幾啱feel 之後又拖住我 感覺係真實得嚟又好唔實實<br />\n之後都有再約出嚟<br />\n最後都係不了了之 佢直頭消失埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個同你傾左兩年 交換過好多個袐密 陪你傾通宵嘅人可以消失得咁突然 就咁樣消失係我嘅生命裏面<br />\n原來少少掛住 少少留戀都冇架 可能大家開始上心佢驚瀨野啦<br />\n所有感情都好脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想知佢到底佢當我係乜<br />\n你應該都唔會睇到依個post架啦 但都希望你唔好再咁對啲女仔 以後遇到啱嘅人就好好地對人 唔係真心鍾意人嘅就唔好搞人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我絕對冇掛住你 我掛住嘅係我地以前嘅開心時光咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝樓主開依個post比我呻吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}